@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ilgqvm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v0 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.62 + v1 + 0.03)) * ((v1 + 0.02 * v0 + 0.69) + (tmp + 0.60 / v2 + 0.32)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.49) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.74)) / wp.exp(tmp))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v2))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.12)
    data[tid] = v0
